headline: Three Reasons to Avoid HRL and One Stock to Buy Instead
summary: Since June 2024, Hormel Foods has been in a holding pattern, posting a small return of 4% while floating around $31.42. The stock also fell short of the S&P 500’s 9.7% gain during that period.
